metadata.name: A.I. Artkorks 001
metadata.description:
Made with StableDiffusion + DallE 2 
2023. 2500x1600px, png.  

I don't even know how to give credit to the things I do. I don't understand if I can say that I did this or not. it's so weird to create things with Artificial Intelligence.  I've been working with digital generative art for years, but this is different. Yes, I did it without a doubt, I'm the only one who has the original file and the rights of the image, but still, how far did I really do it? 

- G. I. Glitchdo.
